115
00:06:17,557 --> 00:06:23,099
is integration of existing innovation,
because, as I said,

116
00:06:23,111 --> 00:06:25,945
Barcelona has always been
on the move for innovation.

117
00:06:26,324 --> 00:06:28,230
So you have
some existing infrastructure,

118
00:06:28,242 --> 00:06:29,844
some existing policies,

119
00:06:31,659 --> 00:06:34,789
existing technical teams
in the municipality.

120
00:06:35,064 --> 00:06:39,581
And when you bring new elements,
such as new information infrastructures,

121
00:06:40,032 --> 00:06:42,553
or new policies,
or new ways of doing,

122
00:06:43,232 --> 00:06:48,170
the first and really big challenge
