which really makes a difference.

124
00:06:51,649 --> 00:06:55,042
This transition is never, never easy
and is never fast.

125
00:06:56,323 --> 00:06:59,194
And this is for Barcelona,
but really for any city.

126
00:07:00,313 --> 00:07:03,076
And this happened, as well,
in the last ten years,

127
00:07:03,076 --> 00:07:08,384
when Barcelona started to try
new technologies.

128
00:07:08,387 --> 00:07:10,604
We have something interesting
in Barcelona

129
00:07:10,621 --> 00:07:14,896
which is called the Urban Lab,
