132
00:07:23,996 --> 00:07:26,518
and work closely
with the municipality

133
00:07:26,542 --> 00:07:29,422
to really find the best users
of this solutions.

134
00:07:29,932 --> 00:07:32,932
So this happened, we had
some learning from there

135
00:07:33,132 --> 00:07:36,187
