164
00:09:34,525 --> 00:09:36,794
How Europe is approaching
the smart cities,

165
00:09:36,806 --> 00:09:38,259
other cities across Europe...

166
00:09:38,284 --> 00:09:41,037
Do you know of any initiative
happening right now?

167
00:09:42,139 --> 00:09:43,894
There's many. There's many.

168
00:09:43,896 --> 00:09:48,533
I know some of them,
but particularly a project,

169
00:09:48,533 --> 00:09:53,122
a European project
which is under a program

170
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:55,758
called "The Lighthouse" project.

171
00:09:56,630 --> 00:10:00,893
We are working actively
with the municipality of Barcelona

172
00:10:01,148 --> 00:10:02,797
on a project called "Grow Smarter".

173
00:10:04,993 --> 00:10:07,882
Let's see, the framework
of this project

174
00:10:08,082 --> 00:10:10,952
is the goal of Europe
and the European commission

175
00:10:11,264 --> 00:10:16,892
to make Europe sustainable
in the short, mid- and long-term.

176
00:10:16,917 --> 00:10:18,581
They started many years ago.

177
00:10:18,593 --> 00:10:21,668
The Lighthouse program is
a specific one

178
00:10:21,705 --> 00:10:24,816
which is tackling
environmental sustainability.

179
00:10:24,978 --> 00:10:27,203
but also economic sustainability,

180
00:10:27,432 --> 00:10:32,638
and it deals a lot
with how we manage and plant cities

181
00:10:32,838 --> 00:10:36,861
today and in the coming years
to fulfil these goals

182
00:10:36,873 --> 00:10:37,987
of sustainability.

183
00:10:37,999 --> 00:10:46,343
So the Lighthouse program promotes
consortiums of European cities

184
00:10:46,368 --> 00:10:50,358
in this case, the "Grow Smarter" project
has three leading cities.

185
00:10:50,370 --> 00:10:51,768
One is Barcelona

186
00:10:51,793 --> 00:10:53,792
the other one is Stockholm,
in Sweden,

187
00:10:53,804 --> 00:10:56,009
and the third is Koln,
in Germany.

188
00:10:57,111 --> 00:11:00,237
Different areas of Europe
with different environmental needs

189
00:11:00,437 --> 00:11:02,139
and environmental realities.

190
00:11:02,151 --> 00:11:06,709
Of course, the Mediterranean has
certain specificities

191
00:11:06,721 --> 00:11:08,080
in terms of climate and so on -

192
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:10,201
different than in Stockholm and Koln.

193
00:11:10,213 --> 00:11:13,222
So that's the first thing
which is interesting of this project.

194
00:11:13,575 --> 00:11:18,922
The objectives are, I would say,
threefold in this case.

195
00:11:18,934 --> 00:11:23,100
It's to try measures
or smart solutions

196
00:11:23,125 --> 00:11:26,489
towards sustainability
in three areas.

197
00:11:26,501 --> 00:11:30,631
The first one is try solutions
or develop solutions

198
00:11:30,831 --> 00:11:33,908
in what we call
"low energy districts".

199
00:11:34,246 --> 00:11:38,500
So, how can we intervene
on buildings, on the streets,

200
00:11:38,700 --> 00:11:39,876
on the energy systems

201
00:11:39,906 --> 00:11:43,668
that the buildings share and use
to make them more efficient

202
00:11:43,673 --> 00:11:48,748
and reduce emissions
and reduce energy consumption?

203
00:11:48,893 --> 00:11:51,610
The second area would be solutions

204
00:11:51,693 --> 00:11:54,859
on integrating
information infrastructures.

205
00:11:55,059 --> 00:11:57,420
So, how can we build,
for example,

206
00:11:57,445 --> 00:12:02,429
city platforms which integrate data
and information resources

207
00:12:02,629 --> 00:12:04,494
in order, again,
to be more efficient?

208
00:12:04,506 --> 00:12:07,270
And the third area
is sustainable mobility,

209
00:12:07,295 --> 00:12:10,718
because, of course,
it's not new to anyone

210
00:12:10,730 --> 00:12:12,901
that mobility is one
of the key issues

211
00:12:12,924 --> 00:12:15,889
in, not only European cities,
but worldwide.

212
00:12:15,901 --> 00:12:22,696
So when we intervene in mobility
and implement efficiency in it,

213
00:12:23,376 --> 00:12:27,356
we will be tackling one
of the most pressing problems

214
00:12:27,368 --> 00:12:28,095
in cities.

215
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:32,721
So the project is trying solutions
at district level

216
00:12:32,921 --> 00:12:33,925
in these three areas.

217
00:12:34,230 --> 00:12:36,718
Great. And, you know,
that was an interesting point

218
00:12:36,955 --> 00:12:40,256
