sustainability or efficiency,

221
00:12:44,912 --> 00:12:45,776
as you mentioned.

222
00:12:45,801 --> 00:12:48,052
And I think, you know,
that's an important point -

223
00:12:48,052 --> 00:12:50,803
that sometimes is missing
in the Smart Cities discourse.

224
00:12:51,535 --> 00:12:52,729
Yes, it's clear.

225
00:12:52,729 --> 00:12:56,124
Actually, you cannot speak
about sustainable

226
00:12:56,136 --> 00:12:59,138
